[1] Cholera - China (Shanghai)
Date: Thu, 20 Oct 2005
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: Eastday.com [edited]
<http://english.eastday.com/eastday/englishedition/metro/userobject1ai1563042.html>

During a municipal press conference on Wed, 19 Oct 2005, the municipal
spokeswoman Jiao Yang unveiled the latest cholera figures. It's 7 cases so
far, according to authoritative statistics.
Jiao Yang commented that the 2005 local epidemic situation of cholera has
eased, compared to the previous years, almost reaching record lows.
[Byline: Gu Jia]
